Enter the following command into the terminal:
    python -m uvicorn main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000


Wait a few seconds and there should be a popup in the bottom right corner, click "Open in browser"


Once you have opened the link, the it will take you to a page that says not found.

Copy the URL of that page, then add /docs to it then press enter, and that will take you to the backend 

For example:

If the original link is https://reimagined-winner-4jp7v5wpgvgfq4p5-8000.app.github.dev/

Then the link to the backend will be https://reimagined-winner-4jp7v5wpgvgfq4p5-8000.app.github.dev/docs

